item.title: Videos from Map Enable
item.description: I took a series of videos of Paul Harrington’s presentation of Map Enable at the last OCC. Some really informative discussion ensued which would be of interest to any startup. Apologies for the sound quality, I really need to get a mini boom mic for my Nokia N95-8GB.
